{"tid":719721,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[慎入] 晨早出門口路邊發現貓屍","createTime":"2018-06-27T15:31:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-28T02:48:02.000Z","uid":43062,"like":0,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b7f58a5eea2ddfa6b38a92989c6ea164cbd90a40","tid":719721,"uid":43062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T15:31:36.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">慎入</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/27/232132_b83676d1290cb363723c6d8f5815feec.png\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F27%2F232132_b83676d1290cb363723c6d8f5815feec.png&d=oW1xjyAySTrJ5ZM6GTBe18PrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=cdc4d0bf\" target=\"_blank\">https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/27/232132_b83676d1290cb363723c6d8f5815feec.png</a><br />\n<br />\n今朝七點幾係街行行下，係馬路欄杆邊見到舊毛茸茸既野，好奇行過去一望，係個死得好恐怖既貓屍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  雙眼突出到好恐怖，口流哂血貼地，個頭方向又好唔正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成貓黎，都算大隻，係寧捨個頭有事<br />\n<br />\n見到之後個心唔舒服左成朝，完全想像唔到隻貓貓經歷咗咩事，流左成口血係地下，忘記唔到個畫面。然後啱先返屋企再經過個度，突然間聽到好淒怨既貓叫聲，成個人即刻起哂雞皮，個種聲係由心入面寒出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d3ee8a839475f3eecc7fbbb7db24da0b4834f29","tid":719721,"uid":162268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T15:34:03.000Z","msg":"咁你又影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n似虐殺feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92563e5d1f0c73cbf4280a464654bd76b9169e88","tid":719721,"uid":146621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T15:57:09.000Z","msg":"唔敢睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9249cde6cd07d7e41ecac513101309b5e87058c1","tid":719721,"uid":43062,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9d3ee8a839475f3eecc7fbbb7d